---
source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Manage content sources

Usage: mf source [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  list    List sources
  add     Add a source
  update  Update a source
  index   Index sources
  remove  Remove a source
  clean   Clean source index

Options:
      --root <PATH>      
      --config <PATH>    
  -v, --verbose...       
  -q, --quiet            
      --format <FORMAT>  [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
      --no-color         
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version
